            <em>pad</em> aθā zī nī humaiiōtara aŋhən <em> be war ī zōhrag barišn ud pad zōhrag dārišn</em>
        </ab>
    <ab>At <em>aθā zī nī humaiiōtara aŋhən</em> he has to bring (the <em>hōm</em> and <em>urwarām</em>) towards the <em>zōhrag</em> and hold them with the <em>zōhrag</em> (cf. <bibl>Kotwal and Kreyenbroek, 2003</bibl>: p. 106 and 109)</ab>
    </Quotations>
